=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Guides_Tour_of_UGens_ex69 ===

DESCRIPTION: A neutral mixed sound, with saw_like oscillator character around 1401 Hz, featuring moderate attack and sustained envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with steep_rolloff character, and spectrally simple.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: moderate
  brightness: neutral
  crest_factor_db: sustained
  envelope_flatness: sustained
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: mixed
  spectral_complexity_mean: simple
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 1400.9498
  harmonic_decay_rate: -2.7945
  harmonic_regularity: 0.8342
  pitch_clarity: 17.7687
  inharmonicity: 0.2791
  type: saw_like
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -7.3632
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: Tour of UGens Example 69
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Guides/Tour_of_UGens.html
// Tags: Tour_of_UGens, Guides
// ---
// --- Example 69 ---
(
{
SinOsc.ar(
            PulseCount.ar(Impulse.ar(10), Impulse.ar(0.4)) * 200,
            0, 0.05
        )
}.play;
)
